thought:
**Analysis of Administrative Unit Change for "Xã Vĩnh Phước, Huyện Tri Tôn, Tỉnh An Giang"**

Okay, so the user wants to know the current administrative unit for "Xã Vĩnh Phước" in An Giang province.  First, I need to isolate the relevant information: "Tỉnh An Giang" and "Xã Vĩnh Phước".  My process will involve reviewing the province's resolutions, specifically focusing on those related to administrative rearrangements.

Initial check on provincial resolutions (60-NQ/TW) shows that An Giang isn't undergoing any province-level changes, so "Tỉnh An Giang" remains unchanged.  Now, I move on to reviewing resolutions concerning ward-level changes within An Giang.

I've got a list of relevant resolutions to check. "1654/NQ-UBTVQH15" looks promising.  I carefully go through the lines within this resolution, and ah, here it is: Line 26: **"Sắp xếp toàn bộ diện tích tự nhiên, quy mô dân số của các xã Vĩnh Phước, Lương An Trà và Vĩnh Gia thành xã mới có tên gọi là xã Vĩnh Gia."** This is definitive. It states that "Xã Vĩnh Phước" is merged into the new "Xã Vĩnh Gia". Perfect. I also checked other relevant resolutions but found no change or matching to the given ward.

With that confirmed, I check the list of new wards for "Xã Vĩnh Gia" in An Giang. I do find a matching record: `{"ward_code":"30568","ward_name":"Xã Vĩnh Gia","province_name":"Tỉnh An Giang"}`. That's what I was looking for.

Therefore, my conclusion, with high confidence, is that "Xã Vĩnh Phước, Huyện Tri Tôn, Tỉnh An Giang" is now part of "Xã Vĩnh Gia" in Tỉnh An Giang. The data will be encoded in the output JSON.
